        <PackageReleaseNotes>
## Patch notes for 149.0.187

These patch notes summarize the changes from version 148.0.136.

Added 13 new endpoints:
* HourlyRate.CreateHourlyRate
* HourlyRate.GetHourlyRates
* HourlyRate.UpdateHourlyRate
* HourlyRate.GetHourlyRate
* HourlyRate.DeleteHourlyRate
* HourlyRate.UpdateHourlyRateValue
* HourlyRatePeriod.GetRatePeriods
* HourlyRatePeriod.CreateRatePeriod
* Risk.GetRisk
* Risk.UpdateRisk
* Risk.RemoveRisk
* Risk.GetRisksForProject
* Risk.CreateRisk

Changes to data models:
* MeetingDetailsDto: Added new field `project`
* MeetingDto: Added new field `project`
* RiskDto: Changed the data type of the field `assignments` from `AssignmentDto` to `RiskAssignmentDto`
* RiskDto: Added new field `project`


        </PackageReleaseNotes>
